    <text>
        <body>
            <pb facs="12180627.jpg"/>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/><placeName corresp="#ANDERNACH">Andernacht</placeName><ref type="gloss_textual" target="andernacht_poem_glosses_textual.php#ANDERNACHTVERSIONGLOSS" /></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>We have wound a weary way</l>
                    <l>Twilights mists are gathering grey</l>
                    <l>Purple now the hills are showing<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">380</add></l>
                    <l>Bright the western clouds are glowing</l>
                    <l>Lashing on with giant force</l>
                    <l>Rolls the <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> his sullen course</l>
                    <l>Flash his waves with flamy red</l>
                    <l>Eddying oer their <name type="geological" corresp="#BASALT">basalt</name> bed<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">385</add></l>
                    <l>Now with wide expanded breast</l>
                    <l>Now between the hills comprest</l>
                    <l>Ever noble, ever free</l>
                    <l>Flows his river majesty</l>
                    <l>Now upon the evening skies<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">390</add></l>
                    <l><placeName corresp="#ANDERNACH">Andernacht</placeName>s hoar ruins rise<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="andernacht_glosses_contextual.php#ANDERNACHTSGREYRUINSGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Memorials of the <placeName corresp="#ROMEANCIENT">Roman</placeName> power<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="andernacht_glosses_contextual.php#ROMANPOWERGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Buttress and battlement and tower</l>
                    <l>Decaying falling fast away</l>
                    <l>The monuments of <persName corresp="#JULIUSCAESAR">Caesar</persName>s sway<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">395</add></l>
                    <l>In heaps together loosely thrown</l>
                    <l>The sculptured head, inscriptioned stone</l>
                    <l>Unguarded now the bridges length</l>
                <pb facs="12180628.tif"/>
                    <l>And failing fast its arches strength</l>
                    <l>The green sod in the moat is growing<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">400</add></l>
                    <l>The cold wind in the chambers blowing</l>
                    <l>And flapping through the thin night air</l>
                    <l>The owl and bat the tenants there</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
        </body>
